Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use and disclose your personal information when you use the Blood Pressure Tool application. We are committed to protecting your privacy and keeping your personal information secure. By using the app, you agree to the collection and use of your personal information as described in this Privacy Policy.
1. Information we collect
When you use the application, we may collect certain information, such as device information, IP address and usage data.
2. Use of information
We use the information we collect to provide you with personalized features and to improve the functionality of the App. Your personal information may be used to generate blood pressure reports, provide health advice and track your progress. We may also use your information to communicate with you and to send you important updates and notices.
3. Data Security
We take appropriate security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure or destruction. We use industry standard encryption techniques and follow best practices to protect your data. Please note, however, that no method of transmission over the Internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
4. Third Party Services
We may use third-party services, such as analytics providers and advertising networks, to assist us in providing and improving the App. These third parties may collect and process your personal information on our behalf, but they are obliged to process your data in accordance with applicable privacy laws and our instructions.
5. Information Disclosure
We do not sell, trade or rent your public information to third parties for marketing purposes.
6. Changes to the Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update or enact this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting a delegate on the app. Your continued use of the app after the change will mean you accept the updated privacy jar.
7. Contact us
If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy or the app's privacy practices, please contact us. We will respond to your inquiry within a reasonable time.
By using Blood Pressure Tool App, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and agree to its terms and conditions.